# whoami terminal: type command, show output, clear, repeat
Output assets/whoami.gif

Set Shell "bash"
Set FontSize 14
Set Width 420
Set Height 280
Set TypingSpeed 60ms
Set Theme "Catppuccin Mocha"

Hide
Type "export PATH=./scripts:$PATH"
Enter
Sleep 200ms
Type "clear"
Enter
Sleep 300ms
Show

Type "whoami"
Enter
Sleep 3s
Type "clear"
Enter
Sleep 600ms

Type "whoami"
Enter
Sleep 3s
